title: New Zealand earthquake drill leads world again (New Zealand Government)
text: ( Source : New Zealand Government ) Initial results show that official sign-ups for New Zealand ShakeOut 2015 have beaten our 2012 national earthquake drill, with over 1.35 million Kiwis signed up this year, says Civil Defence Minister Nikki
